Comment: 0,0:00:52.62,0:00:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,------------------------------IN「揺れ恋ゆららか」----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.12,0:20:19.95,Text-jp-top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,240)\fax-0.1}愛しくて泣いた　あの空は見ていた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.95,0:20:25.71,Text-jp-top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,240)\fax-0.1}まばたきするほど　分からなくなるのが一目惚れ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.71,0:20:32.00,Text-jp-top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,240)\fax-0.1}好きと恋のあいだ　真っ直ぐ見つめて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:37.51,Text-jp-top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,240)\fax-0.1}赤く染まった　私の心ゆら揺れてゆららかに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:40.18,Text-jp-top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,240)\fax-0.1}ひとりだけなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.64,0:20:43.51,Text-jp-top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,240)\fax-0.1}分かってなんてないでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.77,0:20:48.35,Text-jp-top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,240)\fax-0.1}特別なきみは　きみは気づかない
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.12,0:20:19.95,Text-ch-top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,240)\fax-0.1}愛你愛到掉眼淚 只能抬頭望天空
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.95,0:20:25.71,Text-ch-top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,240)\fax-0.1}就在一眨眼之間 莫名其妙一見鍾情？
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.71,0:20:32.00,Text-ch-top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,240)\fax-0.1}喜歡與戀愛的間隙 緊緊盯著不放
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.00,0:20:37.51,Text-ch-top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,240)\fax-0.1}我這通紅的真心 搖來搖去像小鹿亂撞
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.96,0:20:40.18,Text-ch-top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,240)\fax-0.1}心裡只有你一個
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.64,0:20:43.51,Text-ch-top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,240)\fax-0.1}你肯定不知道吧
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.77,0:20:48.35,Text-ch-top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,240)\fax-0.1}如此特別的你 不會發現我的心意
Comment: 0,0:01:18.98,0:01:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,------------------------------OP「Now On Air」----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.27,0:01:22.81,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢の続きをリライト
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.81,0:01:26.19,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}聞こえますか？未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.19,0:01:31.57,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}君と声を重ねて届ける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.57,0:01:40.33,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}はじまりのナンバー　夢にとどけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:45.46,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}平坦な道　探して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:48.76,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}進むことに飽きたの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:51.76,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}叶えても　叶うだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.76,0:01:56.72,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢はなぜこの手で　形を変えてくの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.72,0:02:02.77,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}教えて　どれくらい？　頑張れば辿り着くの…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.77,0:02:08.07,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}理想につぶれてた　私はもういない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:11.53,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢の先をリライト
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.53,0:02:14.74,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}掴みたいよ未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.74,0:02:22.12,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}君と声を重ねて　届けるの　もっと先へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:25.21,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}ひとりじゃ歩けない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:28.38,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}景色　君とみてみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.38,0:02:31.67,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}ひとりじゃ進めない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:34.30,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}直感を信じて生きてたい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:37.39,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢の先の New World
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.39,0:02:40.64,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}聞こえていますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:44.56,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}この声が終わるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:48.44,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}君に伝え続けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.27,0:01:22.81,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}重寫夢想的續集
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.81,0:01:26.19,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}會聽到未來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.19,0:01:31.57,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}我們的聲音重疊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.57,0:01:40.33,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}送出的開場曲 飛向夢想吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:45.46,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}總是尋找平坦的路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:48.76,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}只會讓我厭倦前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:51.76,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}就算去實現 也只是完成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.76,0:01:56.72,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢想為何會因為這隻手改變形態呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.72,0:02:02.77,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}請告訴我 還要努力多久才能到達
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.77,0:02:08.07,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}曾經只能仰視理想的我 已經改變
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:11.53,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}重寫夢想的延續
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.53,0:02:14.74,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}希望把握住未來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.74,0:02:22.12,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}我們的聲音重疊 直抵更遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:25.21,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}一個人走不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:28.38,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}想和你一同欣賞美景
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.38,0:02:31.67,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}一個人無法前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:34.30,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}希望能追隨直覺活著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:37.39,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢想前方的新世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.39,0:02:40.64,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}你聽清楚了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:44.56,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}直到無法發聲為止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:48.44,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}我都會一直為你開口
Comment: 0,0:22:05.01,0:22:08.18,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,---------------------------ED「STAND BY YOU」------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.18,0:22:13.56,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}Stand by me, you did that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.56,0:22:16.19,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}Stand by you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.40,0:22:26.12,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}気持ち伝えるのにいつも何故　こんなにも悩み
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.12,0:22:29.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}ゆらり揺れている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.29,0:22:36.04,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}本当は君が好きなのに　うらはらで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.04,0:22:39.71,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}上手く言えないよ　ねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.63,0:22:42.43,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}振り返れば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:45.60,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}君が映る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.68,0:22:49.35,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}目と目合わせ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.35,0:22:54.44,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}愛の歌　そう唄い出す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.44,0:23:00.65,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}君にいつか届くまでね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.65,0:23:03.24,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}大事にしてたフィーリング
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.24,0:23:05.70,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}全部込めるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.70,0:23:10.70,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}ちゃんと受け止めてくれるよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.70,0:23:15.96,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}真夜中のラブソングで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.96,0:23:21.92,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}世界がちょっと変わってほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.92,0:23:27.30,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}そして君とsweetie　2人ぼっち
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:29.97,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}100ミリちょっとの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.97,0:23:32.06,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}隙間埋める
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.06,0:23:33.89,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}be with you
Comment: 0,0:22:08.18,0:22:13.56,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,Stand by me, you did that
Comment: 0,0:22:13.56,0:22:16.19,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,Stand by you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.40,0:22:26.12,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}只是表明心意 為什麼讓我如此煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.12,0:22:29.29,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}總是搖擺不定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.29,0:22:36.04,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}其實那麼喜歡你 卻言不由衷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.04,0:22:39.71,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}找不到合適的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.63,0:22:42.43,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}回首身後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:45.60,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}眼中有了你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.68,0:22:49.35,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}我們四目相對
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.35,0:22:54.44,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}唱響這首愛之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.44,0:23:00.65,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}希望有一天你能聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.65,0:23:03.24,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}一直珍惜的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.24,0:23:05.70,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}都包含其中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.70,0:23:10.70,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}你一定會接受它吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.70,0:23:15.96,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}願這首午夜小情歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.96,0:23:21.92,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}可以讓世界稍微改變
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.92,0:23:27.30,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}然後與你甜甜蜜蜜 二人世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:29.97,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}十多公分的間隙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.97,0:23:32.06,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}全都被填滿
Comment: 0,0:23:32.06,0:23:33.89,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,be with you
